1
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,680
<font color="#ffffff">I want you</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

2
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,360
<font color="#ffffff">to blend in and befriend Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

3
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,320
<font color="#ffffff">What for?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

4
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,200
<font color="#ffffff">Find out if he's secretly seeing Dao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

5
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:33,760
<font color="#ffffff">PREVIOUSLY</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

6
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:36,160
<font color="#ffffff">I'm giving them to you, buddies.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

7
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,680
<font color="#ffffff">Please accept me as a friend.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

8
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:41,280
<font color="#ffffff">I don't really have many friends.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

9
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,800
<font color="#ffffff">All right.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

10
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,040
<font color="#ffffff">Friends</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

11
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,840
<font color="#ffffff">are better than enemies.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

12
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,920
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Nop.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

13
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,040
<font color="#ffffff">Mr…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

14
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,400
<font color="#ffffff">He's burning up! Mr. Nop is sick.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

15
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:58,320
<font color="#ffffff">Please come over and take care of him.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'll send you the location.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

16
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,960
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you so much. I'll be right there.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

17
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:14,880
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

18
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,519
<font color="#ffffff">How is my dad?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

19
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,120
<font color="#ffffff">Your dad has pneumonia.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

20
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:21,600
<font color="#ffffff">The doctor told him to rest</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and take his medication.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

21
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,240
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you so much.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

22
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,280
<font color="#ffffff">It's okay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

23
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,600
<font color="#ffffff">I'm going to grab some coffee.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

24
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,040
<font color="#ffffff">You go in and see him.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

25
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,720
<font color="#ffffff">He's been calling your name</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">the whole time.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

26
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,240
<font color="#ffffff">Dad…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

27
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,800
<font color="#ffffff">Make it to graduation.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

28
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:19,480
<font color="#ffffff">Apply for scholarships abroad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

29
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:22,680
<font color="#ffffff">With a degree,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">you'll be a respected mechanic.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

30
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,720
<font color="#ffffff">You'll have a respectable desk job.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

31
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,520
<font color="#ffffff">You won't drive a taxi like me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

32
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,400
<font color="#ffffff">I'm heading to work, son.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

33
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,080
<font color="#ffffff">Stay focused, my to-be head mechanic.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

34
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,240
<font color="#ffffff">All right, Dad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

35
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,400
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry, Dad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

36
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,040
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

37
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,080
<font color="#ffffff">Hey.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

38
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,840
<font color="#ffffff">Leaving so soon?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

39
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,240
<font color="#ffffff">I'll prepare for the gig.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

40
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,200
<font color="#ffffff">Isn't it because you're avoiding your dad?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

41
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,840
<font color="#ffffff">Why?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

42
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,400
<font color="#ffffff">What's the problem?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

43
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,720
<font color="#ffffff">It's my family's business.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

44
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,560
<font color="#ffffff">He's been calling out only for you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

45
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,880
<font color="#ffffff">Why don't you think</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">about how happy he'd be<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

46
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,960
<font color="#ffffff">if he woke up and saw your face?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

47
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,080
<font color="#ffffff">Stop assuming things, Dao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

48
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:26,320
<font color="#ffffff">You're the one who likes to think for me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

49
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,760
<font color="#ffffff">And now, you're thinking for him too.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

50
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,560
<font color="#ffffff">Seriously, let me ask you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

51
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:33,920
<font color="#ffffff">What do you think</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Nop and I want from you?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

52
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:37,600
<font color="#ffffff">Fame? Money? Success? Is that it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

53
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,200
<font color="#ffffff">What are you talking about?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

54
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:44,920
<font color="#ffffff">Let me tell you something.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

55
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,800
<font color="#ffffff">You don't have to be perfect.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

56
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:51,000
<font color="#ffffff">Everyone already loves you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

57
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,240
<font color="#ffffff">Stop it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

58
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,760
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not worthy of anyone's love.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

59
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,080
<font color="#ffffff">-Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Thanks.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

60
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,920
<font color="#ffffff">For the lecture.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

61
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,640
<font color="#ffffff">But if you would be so kind,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

62
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,520
<font color="#ffffff">please don't tell my dad I was here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

63
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,120
<font color="#ffffff">Dao?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

64
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,000
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Nop.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

65
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,440
<font color="#ffffff">How are you?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

66
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:38,320
<font color="#ffffff">How are you feeling?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

67
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,560
<font color="#ffffff">Right now,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

68
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,240
<font color="#ffffff">I feel a bit weak…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

69
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:47,040
<font color="#ffffff">but the chills are gone.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

70
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,400
<font color="#ffffff">That's good.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

71
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:52,520
<font color="#ffffff">Do you want to eat anything?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Are you hungry?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

72
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,440
<font color="#ffffff">No.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

73
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,560
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not hungry.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

74
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,840
<font color="#ffffff">By the way…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

75
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:02,360
<font color="#ffffff">how did I get to the hospital?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

76
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:07,760
<font color="#ffffff">I called you several times,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">but you didn't answer,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

77
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:11,200
<font color="#ffffff">so I went to your house</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and found you unconscious with a fever.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

78
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:13,080
<font color="#ffffff">I rushed you to the hospital.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

79
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,760
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you so much, Dao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

80
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:20,920
<font color="#ffffff">You've been very good to me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

81
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,760
<font color="#ffffff">It's nothing at all.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

82
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,760
<font color="#ffffff">I'm always happy to help you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

83
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,720
<font color="#ffffff">If Petch were here,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

84
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,720
<font color="#ffffff">you wouldn't have to go through</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">all this trouble.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

85
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:39,919
<font color="#ffffff">Well…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

86
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,799
<font color="#ffffff">Come to think of it…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

87
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:49,360
<font color="#ffffff">I thought I heard Petch's voice</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">faintly in my ear.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

88
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:53,520
<font color="#ffffff">Did he come see me here?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

89
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,840
<font color="#ffffff">Dao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

90
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,600
<font color="#ffffff">What's wrong?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

91
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,360
<font color="#ffffff">It's nothing.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

92
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:06,000
<font color="#ffffff">Petch didn't come here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

93
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,640
<font color="#ffffff">Right.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

94
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,640
<font color="#ffffff">I don't even know</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

95
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,440
<font color="#ffffff">where he is.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

96
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:21,000
<font color="#ffffff">So how could he possibly visit me?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

97
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,280
<font color="#ffffff">I must have been hallucinating</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">from the fever.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

98
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:40,080
<font color="#ffffff">Hello, Mr. Sompob.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

99
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,200
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Dao.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

100
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:43,080
<font color="#ffffff">I have an urgent job</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I need your help with.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

101
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:46,000
<font color="#ffffff">Do you have time to see me at the office?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

102
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,120
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, I'll be there.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

103
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,880
<font color="#ffffff">I'll head over right now. Goodbye.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

104
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,720
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Nop.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

105
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,880
<font color="#ffffff">I have to excuse myself to go to work now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

106
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,720
<font color="#ffffff">Go ahead, Dao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

107
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:02,400
<font color="#ffffff">Don't worry about me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

108
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,360
<font color="#ffffff">Of course, I'm worried.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

109
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:07,160
<font color="#ffffff">I'll hire a private nurse</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to look after you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

110
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:10,480
<font color="#ffffff">And once I'm done with work,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'll hurry back.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

111
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:13,360
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you very much.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

112
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,040
<font color="#ffffff">I'll get going now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

113
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,480
<font color="#ffffff">Goodbye.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

114
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:18,640
<font color="#ffffff">Okay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

115
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,800
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

116
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:30,360
<font color="#ffffff">Even though you're not here,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

117
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,440
<font color="#ffffff">Dao took such good care of me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

118
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,960
<font color="#ffffff">Do you even realize…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

119
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:42,240
<font color="#ffffff">you've found the best person ever?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

120
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:49,480
<font color="#ffffff">-It was like--</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Joke.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

121
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:53,280
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, my beautiful Sai Kaew.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">What's the matter?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

122
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,280
<font color="#ffffff">Akekaphol wants to see you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

123
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,640
<font color="#ffffff">Really?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

124
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:00,120
<font color="#ffffff">Luck is finally on my side.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

125
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,200
<font color="#ffffff">Thanks.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

126
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,520
<font color="#ffffff">-Wait. Not that way.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-What?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

127
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:07,240
<font color="#ffffff">Akekaphol's office is this way.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

128
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:10,200
<font color="#ffffff">Who said that? He's waiting</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">in the dressing room over there.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

129
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:12,000
<font color="#ffffff">-The dressing room?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Yes.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

130
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,800
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you, sweetheart.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

131
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:21,760
<font color="#ffffff">Did you see the message I sent you, sir?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

132
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:25,000
<font color="#ffffff">If so, you can transfer</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">the additional payment to me now.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

133
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:27,000
<font color="#ffffff">I'm waiting.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

134
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,800
<font color="#ffffff">Sure thing.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

135
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,360
<font color="#ffffff">I'll transfer you some punches</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

136
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,920
<font color="#ffffff">and kicks until you're on the ground.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

137
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,320
<font color="#ffffff">What? Dam?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

138
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,000
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you here?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

139
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:39,000
<font color="#ffffff">Did you trick me?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

140
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,680
<font color="#ffffff">Where are you running off to,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">you sneaky fox?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

141
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,480
<font color="#ffffff">Stop. Stop right there.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

142
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:46,520
<font color="#ffffff">Dam, Sai.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">The three of us are friends, right?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

143
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,960
<font color="#ffffff">Right?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

144
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:50,600
<font color="#ffffff">Friends don't betray each other, Joke!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

145
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,920
<font color="#ffffff">A wolf in sheep's clothing!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

146
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:58,640
<font color="#ffffff">That hurts!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

147
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,880
<font color="#ffffff">How can you accuse me like this?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

148
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:03,040
<font color="#ffffff">You don't even have proof!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Where's the proof?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

149
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,800
<font color="#ffffff">Proof?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

150
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:10,320
<font color="#ffffff">Here! The message</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">you were supposed to send to Ake.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

151
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,960
<font color="#ffffff">I OVERHEARD PETCH ON THE PHONE…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

152
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,600
<font color="#ffffff">Joke!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

153
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:17,120
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you so stupid?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

154
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,240
<font color="#ffffff">I might as well just die.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

155
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,360
<font color="#ffffff">Not yet.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

156
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,320
<font color="#ffffff">You can't die yet.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

157
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:24,640
<font color="#ffffff">You haven't spat out all your poison.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

158
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:28,400
<font color="#ffffff">Dam, I don't know anything.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I really don't!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

159
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:31,160
<font color="#ffffff">Tell us what Akekaphol ordered you to do.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

160
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,920
<font color="#ffffff">-Tell us!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-I don't know anything!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

161
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,000
<font color="#ffffff">I really don't!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

162
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:39,160
<font color="#ffffff">-If you won't speak, your phone will!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-No! Sai Kaew!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

163
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,840
<font color="#ffffff">-Hold him down! Hand it to me!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Give it back!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

164
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:44,080
<font color="#ffffff">Give it back!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

165
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:46,000
<font color="#ffffff">Ouch! No!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

166
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,760
<font color="#ffffff">Sai Kaew, no! I don't know!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

167
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,360
<font color="#ffffff">Dam!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

168
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,200
<font color="#ffffff">Joke lied to us!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

169
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,640
<font color="#ffffff">He smashed Petch's guitar!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

170
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,960
<font color="#ffffff">He did?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

171
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:59,680
<font color="#ffffff">Look. The proof is right here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

